window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Beauty. Desire. And the ability to change the war.</p> <p>David’s first mission as Fieldmaster may also be his last. But it’s not just the Coalition depending on him, it’s the women who’ve sworn their hearts and lives.</p> <p>The enemy is cunning, the battlefield treacherous, and temptation threatens to fracture the bonds between them. David is determined that nothing—not war or ghosts of the past—will tear them apart.</p> <p>Victory could mean a long-awaited ceasefire. Defeat could mean death for everyone he loves.</p> <p>Every choice matters. And David swears he’ll bring his family back.</p>"; 
